column5: Got into some Laker action on Simcoe To-Day.  Couple of Fatties one Male and one Female      Hump Back Creeper Got er Done again To-Day!!!   Travelling today was sled only LOTS of Snow out there!!!  Earlier in the week the Bikes, with one up, were getting out!! But today the only thing I saw out there were Sleds.  The Slush that we found last Sat and Sun was tightened up by Tues Wed and still today we found vey little slush!!  The sleds are running on Top. However with all this snow more slush might show up!!  Have Fun out There and Play Safe  Rick
Great report and pic Rick  Nice and fat lakers... congratulations  Thanks for sharing Leechman
Nice Lakers!  Gotta love when a plan comes together
Some nice respectable lakers there.  Good job.  Joey
nice lakers!!! wish i could have got into some like that on sunday
Nicely done, Rick   Was Larry out there too?  I might..just MIGHT be out there Sunday...I'll keep an eye out for ya if I am!
those are some awsum lookin lakers!  thanks for the pics!  good to see someone can catch em' still not in season here yet!!!!!!!
Johnnyb   Larry was out there!!!!  I won't be out again until next week.  Lots of snow on top!!  Have FUN   Bass    Are you in North Bay??  or Where are Lakers not in Season??  Rick
